kpi_info.title: UL_IOT_PUSCH_DIST_BIN_0 (M8005C317)
kpi_info.use: This measurement provides the 50 percentile value of the uplink Interference Power over Thermal (IoT) Noise Power for the PUSCH Resource Block (RB) distribution bin 0. To increase the granularity, the counter is reported in 10* dB units. To support the PUSCH RB distribution, there are 9 bins (bin0 to bin8). The PUSCH RBs would be evenly distributed (as much as possible) across the 9 bins with bin 0 and bin 8 having an equal number of PUSCH RBs. UPDATED: This measurement is updated by calculating the IoT every sample period the noise measurement is received as per the PUSCH RB distribution bin 0 and taking the 50 percentile value at the end of the collection interval.
